Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:47.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い事　揺れる音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとひそめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:58.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頬のそばで舞う雪達…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:05.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たくさんの後悔　過去を結ぶ笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風のささやき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:11.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れて溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:19.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冬空の淋しさを重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:27.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさの瞳越えて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:35.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいメロディ　指差した一番星光る空に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:43.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描き集めた未来　かじかんだ指の隙間通る星座たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:51.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　この場所から見た景色　叶えたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:57.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束ね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:47.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的願望  搖曳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:58.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓飛雪滑過臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:05.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揮之不去的後悔  緊繫過去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:11.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一觸即散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:19.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夾雜著寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:27.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越過了眼中的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:35.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在想給你的旋律  遙指著初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:43.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼湊出的未來  手指間露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:51.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要實現在此看見的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:57.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在漣漪的水面深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映著蔚藍的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未來又將飄零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季節長存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們編織命運之絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻從來都不曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這絲線將通向何處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(僅僅佇立於此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每當我與他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靈感乍現時的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已經隱約察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終會有結束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終有漸漸打開之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好時光關入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不過我會在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}寫下一句「我沒事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經說過好多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這忽然是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒睡醒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天收拾搬家的行李弄到很晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:00:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到剛才我都跟諾艾爾一起在天文臺的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也認識的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還幫我救了諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳這麼說也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  能看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:08.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(418,270)}「沒有飛碟的小鎮」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始妳怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從東京過來的長途旅行累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是暑假？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…已經下過雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  妳夢裡的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到家之後  稍微休息一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  妳還記得家在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來觀光的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  在哪裡見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可能會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…剛才大家還一起在天文臺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文臺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是乃乃香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候開始就沒見過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香什麼都沒說就從小鎮上消失了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很擔心妳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…七年前的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了這麼久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  妳不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到剛才為止明明還是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但諾艾爾消失了  飛碟也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我不是很明白那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能再會真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外國人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五個人一起聚集在天文臺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常在那裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊太還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後大家一起做的那件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚飛碟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牽著手圍成圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許下願望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟什麼的  怎麼可能會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是相信著的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上不是什麼都沒有發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有這麼想過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個時候  飛碟真的出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  妳為什麼會知道我的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然記得  小時候還一起在天文臺玩耍來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡  裝了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  做得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  不介意的話  之後一起去湖邊發射試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起發射過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候  聚集在天文臺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起呼喚飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  做過這樣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟真的出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟來到小鎮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香妳居然會說這種笑話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟  諾艾爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一點都記不得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳  回憶起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重要的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去問一下湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我們交換聯繫方式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳  柚季  我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  請問住這裡的戶川汐音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  這裡沒有這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  妳在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒人知道飛碟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}優子  妳去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是  騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還記得諾艾爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李全都搬進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們一起大掃除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說  從一開始就沒來過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋兩個  半熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}下一條新聞…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開學典禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在同一個班就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫古宮乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宮同學因為父親工作的原因  從東京轉學過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要和她好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宮同學  妳的座位在第二列的最後一行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在同一個班  真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  難得乃乃香回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去哪裡玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我有事想告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於天文臺的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  要叫上湊太嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想知道乃乃香妳到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後  汐音她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道她在哪個班級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的時候  她搬去很遠的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音一直想見妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}抱歉  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有聯繫方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  是的  現在我們去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和汐音  5個人一起呼喚飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在可能記不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在我所知道的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個在湖上空的飛碟和名叫諾艾爾的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說我們都忘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟小鎮  大家也都是曾有目共睹的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香是在天文臺認識的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到現在也還是最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很想相信妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的會有飛碟來實現大家的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是件非常美好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也很想相信乃乃香說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼事都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是關於諾艾爾的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和諾艾爾一起度過的時光裡發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話語  表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只想起來一點點也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  諾艾爾會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不想用這種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這會不會只是妳的臆想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為記得那個叫諾艾爾的人的…只有乃乃香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  妳夢裡的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾為了實現大家的願望…明明那麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  湊太也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都曾見過那樣的諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  再說下去也沒有意義了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  湊太  能不能不用這種語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊太說的對  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一個人待一會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}諾艾爾是真實存在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有我記得諾艾爾了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連我也忘記了諾艾爾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或許真的就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下所有…我關於諾艾爾的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明能飛得更高的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底少了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會如此焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  一直守護著這座小鎮的你應該是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們或許失去了  最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾  我想見妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳了  快出現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次在我面前歡笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…會發生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的全部都是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾真的不存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  七年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎  小時候曾在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所記得的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所記得的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在流星雨之夜見到的
